  <Summary>Red Sonja Berserker: Sonja rescues and raises a snow bear in Eiglophian Mountains. Years later in Dinander, she seeks work as a sword for hire but is thrown into jail for fighting by Lord Pravus. Pravus sells her to Valtus to be used in the arena to fight wild beasts. Sonja is pitted against her bear who recognises her. Together they fight free and flee to the forest. However the bear is mortally wounded. Sonja returns to Dinandar to feed Valtus to his beasts and to unleash the beasts on the citizens of Dinander.

</Summary>
